      "rdf:value": "<L>107030<pc>541,1<k1>nirdara<k2>nir—dara<h>1<e>3\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>nir—dara</s> ¦ <lex>mfn.</lex> (<ab>fr.</ab> √ <s>df</s> [?]; <ab>cf.</ab> <s>-dawa</s>) pitiless, hard, shameless<info lex=\"m:f:n\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
